    <p> Hey people <br> Today another message at the end of an exciting month in Sydney. As an attentive reader, you will now ask yourself "Why still Sydney?". I just say so much: plans change and sometimes faster than you can look. But more about that later! </p>
    <p> Well, a lot has happened next to work this month. But let's catch the little things that have sweetened the day. Working here in Sydney with the nice colleagues is more and more fun. Somehow I could get used to it. My boss decided that we should all do something unforgettable together. We got 3 options. </p>
