    <p> After the slaughter we all went out to eat together and enjoyed the pleasantly warm afternoon. </p>
    <p> A few days later, one of my colleagues invited us all of us at home for the hot pot. The evening was very nice. My colleague Ray with his wife in an apartment on the 10th floor with a view over the bay, on the Harbor Bridge and Sydney's city center. Simply breathtaking. The Hot Pot Essen is comparable to raclette. The only difference is that there is no grill in the middle, but a large saucepan is in which a soup simmer and that the ingredients are frozen on the table. So you cook your dinner in the soup itself. It was definitely great and I really enjoyed the evening. </p>
    <p> Furthermore, I was lucky enough to get two great photo opportunities in front of the camera in Sydney this month. At first I was lucky to get into an Indian color festival in the best weather and the camera. So I took over 270 photos in about 5 minutes. In the end there were some very nice and two outstanding photos that are worth processing. Here is one to feed. </p>
    <p> The second photo motif is much larger and takes place in Sydney every year for 3 whole weeks. The festival is called Vivid and, in my opinion, is the most impressive festival of everyone. Vivid is also a light and color festival. Only it is more about buildings and art. For example, the opera in Sydney is illuminated very spectacularly - with a 15 -minute animation. Many other buildings, bridges and squares are illuminated and attract thousands of people every evening. I was able to take some really great photos of the opera. In the last few days I hope to come to the opera here in Sydney again after sunset to take more photos. </p>
    <p> OK. Then I will now dissolve the riddle about my renewed plan change. As mentioned above, I will stay here for a few more days. This is because my mother is on the way here. So now very slowly and from the front. About 4 weeks ago my mum called me and told me very proudly that her employment contract would be extended. In the subordinate clause, she said something from 4 weeks remaining vacation she still has to take. By chance, your vacation started almost exactly two weeks after my planned travel start. </p>
